16
00:00:50,135 --> 00:00:54,472
What's the matter, <i>Liebchen,</i> you're sick?

17
00:00:54,973 --> 00:00:56,933
So pale you look.

18
00:00:58,059 --> 00:01:01,020
Tell Mama what's wrong.

19
00:01:01,604 --> 00:01:03,148
(SHIVERING AND GRUNTING)

20
00:01:03,648 --> 00:01:07,152
You don't have to tell. I know.

21
00:01:07,318 --> 00:01:10,905
<i>Life is hard when you're special.</i>

22
00:01:11,072 --> 00:01:13,575
<i>And you are so special.</i>

23
00:01:13,742 --> 00:01:18,037
So clever, so handsome.

24
00:01:18,496 --> 00:01:22,667
(GASPS) <i>When you are older with a stick,</i>

25
