Docile. Friendly.

33
00:01:52,238 --> 00:01:53,323
Appetite?

34
00:01:53,490 --> 00:01:54,991
Low, but I'm not concerned.

35
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:59,788
Hmm, I'm curious to see
how he responds to adverse stimuli.

36
00:02:00,872 --> 00:02:04,709
Let's move on to the ice cream test.

37
00:02:10,965 --> 00:02:12,050
(GRUNTS)

